1. *Budućnosti* su neizvesne. (The futures are uncertain.)
2. Oni su se trudili da unaprede *budućnosti* svoje dece. (They tried to improve the futures of their children.)
3. Uveren je da će njegov rad doprineti boljoj *budućnosti*. (He is confident that his work will contribute to a better future.)
4. Oni su optimistični oko *budućnosti* sveta. (They are optimistic about the future of the world.)
5. Oni su se dogovorili da grade lepšu *budućnost*. (They agreed to build a brighter future.)